Class SaavnStreamingKey

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class SaavnStreamingKey
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<SaavnStreamingKey>
    The SaavnStreamingKey class is used as the Output Key class for the Mapper class SaavnStreamingMapper .

    A Map Output Key is constructed using an object of this class.

    It contains trendingDay and songId as its members and overrides the following methods:

    readFields()

    write()

    hashCode()

    compareTo()
